title: Maan Maryada
subTitle: Yogesh, a selfless man, takes care and raises his two step-brothers, a step-sister and an orphan boy. However, when things go south and he becomes bankrupt, his step-siblings abandon him.

title: Sathi Hara
subTitle: Kundan, a nomad, is offered a music deal when his songs are noticed by a pair of music directors. His lover, Rupa, convinces him to accept it but misunderstandings cause a rift in their relationship.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: To deal with the battle, Parvati takes the form of Adi Shakti and attacks Taraki with fire. Rage and vengeance ignite within Tarakasura.

title: Arshinagar
subTitle: Ranajit and Julekha belong to rival families who have been enemies for years. However, when they meet, there is an unbeatable connection that eventually turns into love.

title: Abbajan
subTitle: A Hindu civil servant's family moves into a predominantly Muslim neighbourhood. Later, when the children befriend a local man, their mother disapproves of their close bond.

title: Aakrosh
subTitle: Samrat, a local thug, constantly protects the people from gangsters like Pannalal. However, many hidden truths about his family tumble out when Subroto, a police officer, is assigned to the area.

title: Phande Poriya Boga Kande Re
subTitle: A light-hearted wedding turns tense when buried family rivalries threaten to explode, testing the resolve of a newly arrived son-in-law.

title: Jamai Raja
subTitle: Realising that marriage is her only path to inheriting her father's fortune, a woman gets married to a poor man who is in desperate need of money.

title: Sasur Bari Zindabad
subTitle: While running away from an arranged marriage, Rupa meets Sonu, a mechanic who changes her life forever.

title: Le Halua Le
subTitle: Sonali moves to the city to earn money and repay her debts to her landlord. She fakes a marriage with Suvojeet, a struggling artist, in order to get low-priced accommodation.

title: Le Halua Le
subTitle: Sonali moves to the city to earn money and repay her debts to her landlord. She fakes a marriage with Suvojeet, a struggling artist, in order to get low-priced accommodation.

title: Hercules
subTitle: A timid Haru refuses to yield his home to thugs, who keep harassing him. However, in a sudden turn of events, he gains Hercules-like strength and fights them.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: To her surprise, Parvati senses a deep connection with the natural environment and realises her true form.

title: Black
subTitle: Bittu, a small-town man, is on a mission to turn his life around and avenge the death of his father, a police officer, who was falsely implicated in a case.

title: Sindurer Adhikar
subTitle: Misunderstandings cause Prijay and Susmita's marriage to fall apart and she moves to her brother Prakash's house. Prijay's illness, however, makes her rethink her decision.

title: Badla
subTitle: Bharti Devi leads a happy life with her three sons, Jay, Sujay and Arjun. However, Sanatan decides to break their family apart in order to settle past scores with Bharti, who he believes wronged him.

title: Awara
subTitle: Surya falls in love with a girl and follows her to Kolkata, where she stays with her rowdy elder brother. Later, he decides to rescue her when he discovers that a gangster wants to marry her forcibly.

title: Jiban Niye Khela
subTitle: In the distant village of Dharampur, Dr Subhankar Sanyal fights the bureaucracy and brings justice to the lives of his patients.

title: Sneher Protidan
subTitle: Mohan loves his brothers a lot and tries to ensure they do well in life. However, all of them fall prey to a misunderstanding, which risks their bond.

title: Total Dadagiri
subTitle: College students Joy and Jonaki fall in love with each other, much to the distress of her father, who is totally opposed to their relationship.

title: Total Dadagiri
subTitle: College students Joy and Jonaki fall in love with each other, much to the distress of her father, who is totally opposed to their relationship.

title: Paapi
subTitle: When Harekrishna offers him a large sum of money, Shambu, a criminal, murders Susanta. Subsequently, his sister Chandra commits suicide due to her love for Susanta.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: While Parvati is delighted with her discovery of her true identity and reveals her affection for Lord Shiva, Tarakasura devises a new conspiracy.

title: Bonku Babu
subTitle: Bonku Babu has absolute control over his household, and even denies permission to his son and daughter-in-law to live separately. Things take a turn when the patriarch meets with an accident.

title: Raktomukhi Neela
subTitle: Byomkesh becomes curious when Ramanath, a jewel thief, is released from Alipur jail. Later, Maharaja Ramendra Singha seeks his help and asks him to investigate the murder of his associate Haripada Rakshit.

title: Naga Panchami
subTitle: A man kills his sister and throws her family into disarray. However, his sister's daughter, a shape-shifting snake, is determined to seek revenge.

title: Kartabya
subTitle: A bridegroom disagrees to marry due to the non-payment of dowry by the bride's father. In spite of his brother's request, he remains stubborn and decides to stop his wedding.

title: Criminal
subTitle: Shiba, an orphan turned criminal, decides to mend his ways after falling in love with a woman named Sanchari. However, circumstances force him to re-enter the world of crime.

title: Bandhan
subTitle: After his wife's demise, a man tries to start over with her estranged family. When he falls in love with his wife's twin, he fears that his efforts to mend broken relations will go to waste.

title: Khiladi
subTitle: Two families of opposing faiths are in a long-standing rivalry over land and past wounds. However, one man vows to reunite them by disguising himself as a Hindu person.
